  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This pilot project aims to give nurses the skills to manage children with neurological disorders in the first critical 72 hours of arrival at Queen Elizabeth Central Hospital, Blantyre, Malawi. The project will target 150 children and develop guidelines for the Ministry of Health and Nursing Council for use in the nurses training curriculum.</narrative>
